{"tid":2033951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"《視訊戀愛風潮》相識、約會到告白都在網路上 現實沒見過面也可以很恩愛","createTime":"2020-05-25T03:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T03:22:29.000Z","uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e39998afc63c29e6a30faa1b976812e09a8b73c","tid":2033951,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_Vlqadq6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_Vlqadq6Y.jpg&h=773e1ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在防疫期間避免現實聚會的情況之下，視訊相關產業因此蓬勃發展起來，像是視訊上課、視訊會議、視訊酒會&hellip;&hellip;既然如此有視訊戀愛也不奇怪了吧？跟以往先經由現實認識再相隔兩地的「遠距離戀愛」不太一樣，這種視訊戀愛從兩人相識、約會到告白全都透過視訊進行，甚至從來沒有在現實面對面見過對方！越來越多人透過這種模式展開戀情，當然代表視訊戀愛有其優點，但是會不會衍生詐騙問題還是令人擔心啊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n視訊戀愛（remove love）最近蔚為風潮！？<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_Vlqadq6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_Vlqadq6Q.jpg&h=a4db0101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_Vlqadq6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_Vlqadq6U.jpg&h=20910ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本富士電視台的晨間情報節目「めざましテレビ」製作了視訊戀愛的專題報導，根據聯誼網站所說，因為疫情影響讓許多熱愛聯誼的男男女女無法舉辦現實聚會，於是就轉而透過視訊服務尋找愛情&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"3b0e6d1eafa7b93c3374f53e08e05777d8be3510","tid":2033951,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"3男3女進行視訊聯誼<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_Vlqadq6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_Vlqadq6Y.jpg&h=773e1ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n許多人一開始不習慣跟不認識的人們開視訊，然而用過幾次以後就深深愛上，因為視訊聯誼可以彌補很多現實聯誼的缺陷&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n不怕忘記每個人的基本資料！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKc.jpg&h=89e8ca80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實聯誼必需耗費腦力記住每個人自我介紹的內容，或者至少要記住自己看上的那個人，不過線上聯誼就可以利用文字聊天室記錄下每個人的基本資料，隨時翻閱不怕忘記！除此之外，想說悄悄話的時候，也不用再找藉口一起去上廁所了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3位男生打開密語視窗說起悄悄話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKg.jpg&h=0da2c47a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偷偷討論自己看上哪一位女生<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKk.jpg&h=5a0dd135&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48cf18552e0cd5932d768f388fe116af7489acb0","tid":2033951,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"記者訪問到一位藉由視訊聯誼交到女朋友的人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n28歲的Y先生，1個多月前交到大1歲的女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKo.jpg&h=de47dfcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKSX.jpg&h=761077f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我們從相識、約會到告白&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKs.jpg&h=f553fbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「全都是透過視訊」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKw.jpg&h=7119f551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「現在一大早起來就打視訊電話給對方」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKSY.jpg&h=baba776c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「一天可能會連續視訊12小時」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadrKSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadrKSZ.jpg&h=3435708f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nY先生與女朋友的賞月約會，相距很遠也可以看著同一個月亮！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadraSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadraSa.jpg&h=b4edacbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nY先生認為視訊約會最大的優點是省去許多溝通協調的心力，可以專心了解對方以及宣傳自己&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「一般的約會都要一直溝通接下來要去哪裡吧？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadraSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadraSb.jpg&h=3a62ab5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「視訊約會就可以一直專心在對話之上，深入了解對方，並且宣傳自己」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_VlqadraSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_VlqadraSe.jpg&h=30a7a247&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97d10c2bbfea162f5639f3a2dd05b498cc77d172","tid":2033951,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"但是視訊當然也有缺點啦，像是少了肢體接觸就必需一直講話才能維繫氣氛，或是同居的家人打擾私密對話，報導播出以後還有網友提出視訊詐騙的危險&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n家人亂入嚴重破壞約會氣氛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_Vl6KbqqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_Vl6KbqqQ.jpg&h=c46501e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/43/00/qJeanZ_Vl6KbqqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F43%2F00%2FqJeanZ_Vl6KbqqU.jpg&h=402f0f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（&deg;Д&deg;&equiv;&deg;Д&deg;）大家可不可以接受跟現實沒見過面的人交往呢？"}]}